file.name: schema.yaml
file.content:
components:
  schemas:
    PlatformInformation:
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
      type: object
info:
  description: ASGI Agent
  title: Example API
  version: '1.0'
openapi: 3.0.0
paths:
  /:
    get:
      description: Home
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/PlatformInformation'
  /jsonrpc:
    post:
      description: RPC
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              example:
                id: 1
                jsonrpc: '2.0'
                method: multiply
                params:
                - 5
                - 5
              properties:
                id:
                  type: integer
                jsonrpc:
                  type: string
                method:
                  type: string
                params:
                  type: object
              type: object
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                example:
                  id: 1
                  jsonrpc: '2.0'
                  result: 25
                properties:
                  id:
                    type: integer
                  jsonrpc:
                    type: string
                  result:
                    type: object
                type: object
          description: result of RPC method
